  <rte>
    <name>The Mosedale Horseshoe from Wasdale Head</name>
    <desc>This Lake District walk should not be attempted by those with little experience of high level walking. Even with experience it should not be attempted in poor visibility if you want to enjoy some of the best scenery in the Lake District. It is a walk that needs to be kept for a fine day!</desc>
    <author>Copyright Walking Britain</author>
	<url>www.walkingbritain.co.uk/walk-1126-description</url>
